HEADWORD: Toadstool
<hw>Toad"stool`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A name given to many umbrella-shaped fungi, mostly of the genus
<gen>Agaricus</gen>. The species are almost numberless. They grow on
decaying organic matter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Toady</ent>⟦br⟧
